  "designNotes": [
    "No USB connector on module -- must add external USB-C connector and D+/D- routing",
    "Castellated pads allow direct soldering to carrier PCB",
    "32 usable GPIOs -- excellent for large matrices or direct-pin wiring",
    "Requires external LiPo charger IC (MCP73831 or TP4056) for battery support",
    "On-module PCB antenna -- keep ground plane clear under antenna area",
    "Must flash bootloader via SWD (J-Link or similar) before USB bootloader works",
    "P0.09 and P0.10 are NFC pins by default -- must disable NFC in firmware config to use as GPIO",
    "Needs custom ZMK board definition -- not a standard ZMK board",
    "Most cost-effective option for custom PCB designs"
  ],
  "features": [
    "32 usable GPIOs — most of any keyboard module",
    "Pre-certified BLE antenna on module",
    "Castellated pads for direct PCB soldering",
    "On-module 32.768kHz and 32MHz crystals",
    "Cost-effective for custom PCB designs ($4.80-8.00)",
    "Full nRF52840 capabilities (1MB flash, 256KB RAM)"
  ],
  "concerns": [
    "No USB connector — must add external USB-C and routing",
    "Requires external LiPo charger IC",
    "Must flash bootloader via SWD before USB works",
    "Needs custom ZMK board definition",
    "NFC pins (P0.09/P0.10) need firmware config to use as GPIO",
    "Keep ground plane clear under antenna area"
  ],
